EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 0800Z TO 1900Z DAILY
   17 THRU 21 NOV WITHIN:
   A. 30 MILES OF 57-28.1N 008-46.5W.
   B. 28 MILES OF 57-35.2N 010-19.3W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR
   PHONE: 187 060 4449 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2684/14(37), OBSTRUCTION REMOVED.
3. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2738/14(36), AIDS RESTORED.
4. CANCEL HYDROLANT 2759/14(37), 2762/14(37),
   OPERATIONS COMPLETED.
5. CANCEL THIS MSG 212000Z NOV 14.
